TC1 Successful Sign In
STR:
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Add valid Username (ex. UserMy) to the 'Username' input field
3. Add valid Password (ex. trust@test.com) to the 'Password' input field
4. Click on the 'Sign In' button

ER:
'Create Post' button is shown


TC2 Successful Sign Out
STR:
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Add valid data to the 'Username' (ex. UserMy) input field
3. Add valid data to the 'Email' (ex. trust@test.com) input field
4. Add valid data to the 'Password' (ex. PassWord2022) input field
5. Click on the 'Sign up for OurApp' btn

ER:
'Hello [Username], your feed is empty.' text is shown

TC3 Finding a post
Preconditions:
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Add valid Username (ex. UserMy) to the 'Username' input field
3. Add valid Password (ex. trust@test.com) to the 'Password' input field
4. Click on the 'Sign In' button

STR:
1. Click on my Profile icon
2. Click on the Search icon
3. Enter 'test' text into the search field
4. Choose any search result item

ER:
Post with the searched text is shown


TC4 Sendind messages
Preconditions:
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Add valid Username (ex. UserMy) to the 'Username' input field
3. Add valid Password (ex. trust@test.com) to the 'Password' input field
4. Click on the 'Sign In' button

STR:
1. Click on the Chat icon
2. Add any text to the input field
3. Press 'Enter' keyboard key

ER:
Message is shown in the chat

TC5 Create post
Preconditions:
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Add valid Username (ex. UserMy) to the 'Username' input field
3. Add valid Password (ex. trust@test.com) to the 'Password' input field
4. Click on the 'Sign In' button

STR:
1. Click on the 'Create Post' button
2. Add any text to the 'Title' input field
3. Add any text into the 'Body Content' input field
4. Click on the 'Save New Post' button

ER:
'New post successfully created.' text is shown

TC5 Delete post
Preconditions:
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Add valid Username (ex. UserMy) to the 'Username' input field
3. Add valid Password (ex. trust@test.com) to the 'Password' input field
4. Click on the 'Sign In' button

STR:
1. Click on the post
2. Click on the trash icon

ER:
'Post successfully deleted' text is shown